ansactions from being published and deal with the time gap between validation and the publishing decision.', 'REQ82': 'As a FABS user, I want to submit a citywide as a PPoPZIP and pass validations.', 'REQ83': 'As a Broker user, I want to have updated error codes that accurately reflect the logic and provide enough information, so that I can fix my submission.', 'REQ84': 'As an agency user, I want to leave off the last 4 digits of the ZIP without an error, so that I can complete my submissions.', 'REQ85': 'As a FABS user, I want to make sure the historical data includes all necessary columns, so that the information in the database is correct.', 'REQ86': 'As a data user, I want to access two additional fields from the FPDS data pull.', 'REQ87': 'As a FABS user, I want additional helpful info in the submission dashboard, so that I can better manage submissions and IG requests.', 'REQ88': 'As a FABS user, I want to download the uploaded FABS file, so that I can get the uploaded file.', 'REQ89': 'As a Developer I want to quickly access Broker application data, so that I can investigate issues.', 'REQ90': 'As a Developer , I want to determine the best way to load historical FPDS data, so that I can load all FPDS data since 2007.', 'REQ91': 'As a FABS user, I want the language on FABS pages to be appropriate for me, so that I am not confused.', 'REQ92': 'As a FABS user, I do not want  DABS banner messages and vice versa, so that I have the appropriate information for my application.', 'REQ93': 'As a FABS user, I want to have read-only access to DABS, so that I can view DABS pages without wanting two sets of permissions.', 'REQ94': 'As a FABS user, I want to have my validations run in a reasonable amount of time.', 'REQ95': 'As a FABS user, I want to see correct status labels on the Submission Dashboard, so that I can quickly see my submission history.', 'REQ96': 'As an agency user, I want to know when the submission periods start and end, so that I know when the submission starts and ends.', 'REQ97': 'As an agency user, I want a landing page to navigate to either FABS or DABS pages, so that I can access both sides of the site.', 'REQ98': 'As an agency user, I want to submit my data elements surrounded by quotation marks, so that Excel won't strip off leading and trailing zeroes.'
