djust workload as necessary and ensure service levels are met', 'REQ37': 'As an Applicant, I want to Request a Plan Review Meeting, so that I can meet with the Plan Review Staff regarding the plan review.', 'REQ38': 'As a Plan Review Staff member, I want to successfully Conduct a Plan Review Meeting with the Applicant and record the outcome, so that I can listen to it again.', 'REQ39': 'As a Plan Review Staff member, I want to Review Plans, so that I can review them for compliance and either approve, or fail or deny the plans and record any conditions, clearances, or corrections needed from the Applicant.', 'REQ40': 'As an Applicant, I want to Resubmit Plans, so that I can review revised plans. ', 'REQ41': 'As a Plan Review Staff Member, I want to Review the Code Modifications submitted by the Applicant, so that I can review the request and if approved, associate it with the appropriate project.', 'REQ42': 'As a Plan Review Staff member, I want to Track the Completion of Required Plan Reviews, so that I can ensure all plan review tasks are completed, results have been sent to the Applicant and any downstream steps are initiated such has a final review or payment for permit issuance.', 'REQ43': 'As a Development Staff member, I want to Issue a Development-related Permit, so that I can grant the request to the Applicant to begin work', 'REQ44': 'As a Staff member, I want to Manage Bonds, so that I can track and manage bonds throughout the lifecycle of the project until release.', 'REQ45': 'As an Applicant, I want to Complete Building Development Project, so that I can receive any posted bond and/or obtain occupancy.', 'REQ46': 'As an Applicant, I want to Complete Building Development Project, so that I can receive any posted bond and/or obtain occupancy.', 'REQ47': 'As a Customer, I want to Request Inspection, so that a County inspector is assigned to perform an inspection of my project.', 'REQ48': 'As an Inspection Staff member, I want to Create an Inspection, so that I can schedule and assign the inspection.', 'REQ49': 'As an Inspection Staff Supervisor, I want to Assign Inspections, so that I can make sure the appropriate Inspector receives the work.', 'REQ50': 'As an Inspection Supervisor, I want to Manage Inspector Workload, so that I can meet service level and quality requirements.', 'REQ51': 'As an Inspector, I want to Conduct Inspections, so that I can validate Customer compliance with code and regulations and provide results of the inspection to the Customer.', 'REQ52': 'As an Enforcement Staff member, I want to Issue a Notice of Violation, so that I can provide formal communication to the responsible party.', 'REQ53': 'As a l Staff member, I want to search for Property information, so that I can obtain all associated current and historic owners, permits, and applications.', 'REQ54': 'As a Staff member, I need to be notified when Geospatial attributes change, so that I can ensure that I am reviewing the permit/application to the most current data and appropriate standards.', 'REQ55': 'As a County Staff Member, I want to create a custom query/report outside of the common querying/reporting functionality, so that I can fulfill a request.', 'REQ56': 'As a Staff member, I want to create each condo unit, so that I can associate it to the child parcel and address after the condominiums are recorded in the system.', 'REQ57': 'As a Technical Staff member, I want to update the GIS Property Management, so that I can successfully update the transactional Parcel Pin to reference the GIS layer where the Split or Merged Parcel Pin exists.', 'REQ58': 'As a Staff member, I want to Send or Post Citations and Fines, so that I can successfully send the Notice Of Violation document to the property owner and log information about the action.'
