 payment status, access and share camp photos, connect with staff in case of emergencies, and have peace of mind knowing that their child is well taken care of and their information is secure.                Camp workers and counselors benefit from CampConnect by having easy access to their assigned campers, their locations, and their daily tasks. They can take attendance, submit completion reports for assigned tasks, report inappropriate behavior of campers, report supply shortages or necessary repairs, and ensure that their responsibilities are fulfilled efficiently.                The primary objectives of CampConnect are to simplify camp administration, improve organization, enhance communication, automate repetitive tasks, reduce paperwork, facilitate parental involvement, and provide a secure and efficient platform for camp management. By meeting these objectives, CampConnect aims to create a seamless camp experience for all stakeholders involved, fostering a positive and well-structured environment for campers, parents, and camp staff.                The end users of CampConnect include camp administrators responsible for managing camp operations, parents enrolling their children in camp and seeking information and updates, camp workers and counselors in charge of campers' well-being and activities, and campers themselves who will benefit from an organized and engaging camp experience. CampConnect caters to the diverse needs of these user groups, promoting effective communication, efficient administration, and an enjoyable camp experience for everyone involved.    ]    Output Format: [        {'QUE1': 'abc?', ..., 'QUE5': 'xyz?'
}        SEP        {'REQ1': 'abc', ..., 'REQ50': 'xyz'
}    ]

